        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 18 at 7:44PM CDT until August 18 at 8:30PM CDT by NWS Houston/Galveston TX</headline>
        <description>SVRHGX

The National Weather Service in League City has issued a

* Severe Thunderstorm Warning for...
North central Harris County in southeastern Texas...

* Until 830 PM CDT.

* At 744 PM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Willowbrook,
or near Greater Greenspoint, moving northwest at 15 mph.

HAZARD...Quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Damage to vehicles is expected.

* Locations impacted include...
Greater Greenspoint, Willowbrook, and Greater Inwood.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

Large hail, damaging wind, and continuous cloud to ground lightning
are occurring with this storm. Move indoors immediately. Lightning is
one of nature's leading killers. Remember, if you can hear thunder,
you are close enough to be struck by lightning.</instruction>
